1
00:01:09,780 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,740 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 5=
(The "Other Man" Arrives)

3
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:31,840
Dear.

4
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:34,079
Recently, Gu Qingmei

5
00:01:34,319 --> 00:01:36,120
has become increasingly unreasonable.

6
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:41,840
Qingmei has always been well-mannered.

7
00:01:42,519 --> 00:01:44,400
Her temperament is
exactly like her mother's.

8
00:01:45,239 --> 00:01:47,079
You are being too harsh on her.

9
00:01:47,519 --> 00:01:48,599
Am I being harsh?

10
00:01:49,519 --> 00:01:51,680
You still can't forget Xia Lan, right?

11
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:54,200
Back then, you couldn't marry
the eldest daughter of the Xia family,

12
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,359
so you had your son marry her daughter

13
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:57,719
to fulfill your dream.

14
00:01:58,359 --> 00:02:00,599
Look at the person
you brought to this family!

15
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:02,480
Nonsense!

16
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:05,599
Am I talking nonsense,
or are you feeling guilty?

17
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,799
You are just projecting your affection.

18
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:08,520
Shut up!

19
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,879
Their marriage

20
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:13,159
concerns the interests
of both of families.

21
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,800
If you still want your son

22
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,520
to inherit the He family's business,

23
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:18,919
you'd better watch your mouth!

24
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:34,560
Madam Gu, you're back.

25
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:37,240
Mr. He isn't back
from his dinner meeting yet.

26
00:02:37,759 --> 00:02:39,039
I made some hangover soup.

27
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,479
Would you like some?

28
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,439
Bring it to my room.

29
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,280
Yes.

30
00:03:17,199 --> 00:03:18,520
(If the jewelry is sold out,)

31
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,120
(then you try to get some more.)

32
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:26,280
(Let me check)

33
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,639
(whether you are the real Gu Qingmei.)

34
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:32,919
What is going on?

35
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:36,599
Why are you here?

36
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:38,719
Why didn't you...

37
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:39,599
Didn't pass out?

38
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:40,879
You...

39
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,439
(Since it was for me,)

40
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,800
(mind taking a sip first?)

41
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:57,639
(I knew there was a catch.)

42
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,759
This works too.

43
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,919
What we did not finish last time,

44
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,520
let's continue today.

45
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:07,439
It will help refresh your memory.

46
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,599
Does your wife know you act like this?

47
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,439
He Jinchuan.

48
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:12,599
He Jinchuan, where are you?

49
00:04:15,820 --> 00:04:16,920
(Xu Niannian)

50
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:17,399
(Xu Niannian)
Hello?

51
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,540
(Xu Niannian)

52
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:19,160
Hello?

53
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:22,680
Say something!

54
00:04:23,439 --> 00:04:24,560
Why is no one speaking?

55
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:33,000
To be honest,

56
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,120
even if I had not lost my memory,

57
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,759
I would not be interested in
someone like you.

58
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,079
Amnesia?

59
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,560
Should we take a look back

60
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,480
at our exciting videos?

61
00:04:44,639 --> 00:04:45,199
Sure!

62
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,319
Then people should watch it together!

63
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,560
After all,
I'm theheir of Gu Corporation.

64
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,920
I don't care about being the mistreated
daughter-in-law of the He family.

65
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,839
But you...

66
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,279
Will Xu Niannian let you off?

67
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:02,160
Get lost!

68
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:03,920
Don't come near me again!

69
00:05:17,399 --> 00:05:17,560
Niannian.

70
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,560
Where have you bee?
You didn't even take your phone.

71
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,319
Niannian,

72
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,920
I sneaked out to the balcony
to have a cigarette.

73
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:23,399
Don't be mad.

74
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,279
So annoying!

75
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:25,480
Don't smok late at night!

76
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:26,399
Let's go.

77
00:05:27,399 --> 00:05:27,959
Wait.

78
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,319
Why do you only smell of perfume

79
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,439
and not of cigarette?

80
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,160
I though you wouldn't like the smell,

81
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,920
so I wore some perfume.

82
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:42,079
Don't be mad.

83
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:43,319
I will never smoke again!

84
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:43,959
I promise!

85
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,639
Really?

86
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,360
Yes, for real.

87
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:45,879
Let's go.

88
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:51,759
Boss.

89
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,800
You are on fire today!

90
00:05:54,199 --> 00:05:55,000
Something good must have happened today.

91
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:55,639
You, you...

92
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,519
Just keep spinning and hitting!

93
00:06:00,199 --> 00:06:01,120
You are right.

94
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,360
The person I am looking for

95
00:06:03,759 --> 00:06:04,720
is not Gu Qingmei.

96
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,240
The records say

97
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:12,600
that Gu Qingmei is allergic to peaches.

98
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:16,079
Yet she ordered a peach juice cocktail

99
00:06:17,079 --> 00:06:19,279
and drank it without
any reaction at all.

100
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:28,199
(Sometimes I am really curious.)

101
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,399
(Who exactly are you?)

102
00:06:32,759 --> 00:06:33,519
So you are saying

103
00:06:33,839 --> 00:06:35,000
she is not Gu Qingmei?

104
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,480
Then who is she?

105
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,560
I'm curious too.

106
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,800
Who exactly is she?

107
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:50,879
Boss, you're making progress!

108
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:52,399
Boss, look at you.

109
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,160
Don't flatter me.

110
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:55,040
No way!

111
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,920
Do rich people wear knockoffs?

112
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,759
I used to be this badly off?

113
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,000
Qingmei.

114
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,279
I heard today is your first day at work.

115
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:06,639
Do you want me to
lend you another outfit?

116
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,600
Again?

117
00:07:08,879 --> 00:07:10,839
You lent me this dress for the auction?

118
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,000
Of course.

119
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,839
Although it is last year's style,

120
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:16,319
it is haute couture.

121
00:07:16,439 --> 00:07:19,040
(She gave me a knockoff to belittle me!)

122
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,839
(Then don't blame me for being unkind!)

123
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:24,399
Then thank you, Niannian.

124
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,759
I have always heard that
you have excellent taste in clothes.

125
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:29,639
I really like all of these.

126
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,040
These...

127
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,560
Why?

128
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,480
You are not reluctant to
part with them, are you?

129
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,079
If so, forget it.

130
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,639
Of course not.

131
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,000
Just some clothes.

132
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,160
That is great!

133
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,879
I'll wash it and give it back to you

134
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,759
after I'm done wearing it.

135
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:46,000
No need.

136
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:46,920
Keep them for yourself.

137
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,480
I never put on

138
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,879
clothes that others have worn.

139
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,639
Wealthy young ladies

140
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:59,279
are indeed best dealt with
by over-praising.

141
00:08:09,839 --> 00:08:10,879
You dressed like that.

142
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:12,920
We know you are going to work,

143
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,240
but others would think
you are going to a fashion show.

144
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,879
After all, I'm now the Chairman
of Gu Corporation.

145
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:18,560
I cannot dress

146
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,240
like a free maid of the He family.

147
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:24,839
Mom.

148
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:27,519
She is the Chairman now.

149
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,439
It is only proper for her
to dress appropriately.

150
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,639
Jinchen.

151
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,720
Why are you speaking up for her again?

152
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,879
I am only stating the facts.

153
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:36,480
Qingmei.

154
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,600
I am on the way.

155
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,519
Let me drive you.

156
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:41,360
Sure. Thank you, dear.

157
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,960
(Gu Corporation)
Well, I can help you with the company.

158
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,480
You don't have to
work so hard every day.

159
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,039
I'm good.

160
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:03,679
Grinding at the office

161
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:05,360
is better than being a workhorse
in the He family.

162
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:08,559
I thought Mr. He and Madam Gu
weren't on good terms?

163
00:09:09,039 --> 00:09:10,840
They seem quite affectionate.

164
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:11,919
Are you out of your mind?

165
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,799
If my husband suddenly
inherited a huge fortune,

166
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:17,080
I would definitely treat him
like a god of wealth too!

167
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:18,960
Good morning, Madam Gu.

168
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:20,519
Good morning, Mr. Mu.

169
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:40,000
I didn't expect to see you here today,
Mr. He.

170
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,639
For business.

171
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:46,000
Finally, Shengda is going to
collaborate with Gu Corporation.

172
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:47,519
That makes sense.

173
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,639
Good things should stay in the family.

174
00:09:51,159 --> 00:09:52,840
Not as fast as Mr. Mu.

175
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,039
You just returned

176
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:57,039
and you already snatched up
shares of Gu Corporation.

177
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:58,519
Not at all.

178
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,000
After all, Shengda has its chairman
at the helm.

179
00:10:01,559 --> 00:10:02,720
There is no room for me to step in.

180
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:04,600
Unlike Gu Corporation,

181
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:06,600
I need to keep an eye on it.

182
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:10,559
I can't let my investment go to waste!

183
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:16,759
50th floor.

184
00:10:24,260 --> 00:10:27,320
(Yunhu Resort Acquisition Plan)

185
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:29,279
(Yunhu Resort Acquisition Plan)
Your group's Yunhu Resort

186
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,200
has been losing money over the years.

187
00:10:30,559 --> 00:10:31,519
Keeping it is just a burden.

188
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,080
Our offer is very reasonable.

189
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,580
(Yunhu Resort Acquisition Plan)

190
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,360
If it is losing money,

191
00:10:39,879 --> 00:10:40,919
why do you want to acquire it?

192
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:42,840
Madam Gu, you may not know this.

193
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:45,519
Although the resort
has been losing money,

194
00:10:46,159 --> 00:10:48,559
the land itself is very valuable.

195
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,799
It's next to the factory
of Meiyan International.

196
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:51,919
Besides,

197
00:10:52,279 --> 00:10:53,639
the last ecological green space

198
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,600
in this suburban area.

199
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,279
Meiyan International?

200
00:11:14,519 --> 00:11:15,759
(The smell is pungent.)

201
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,320
(What kind of raw material is it?)

202
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,320
(Why do I have this part of memory?)

203
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:25,919
Since it involves ecological
and environmental issues,

204
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,840
I believe it should not be
over-commercially developed.

205
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,440
So for the resort,

206
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:30,840
we are not selling it.

207
00:11:40,039 --> 00:11:41,600
You two are quite in sync!

208
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,720
I am just analyzing the
situation objectively.

209
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,919
The decision is Madam Gu's.

210
00:11:52,399 --> 00:11:52,960
Qingmei,

211
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,840
I am also thinking
about your best interests.

212
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,799
Getting rid of these loss-making burdens

213
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,000
is good for Gu Corporation

214
00:11:59,519 --> 00:12:00,360
and for you.

215
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:01,480
Besides...

216
00:12:02,180 --> 00:12:04,380
(Manager Lin)

217
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:11,919
Got it.

218
00:12:12,159 --> 00:12:12,919
I will be right there.

219
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:15,919
There is an emergency at the company.

220
00:12:16,279 --> 00:12:17,120
I have to go and deal with it.

221
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:20,759
This acquisition plan...

222
00:12:21,159 --> 00:12:22,639
Please consider it carefully.

223
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:24,360
Alright.

224
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,759
Goodbye, Mr. He.

225
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:29,840
Mr. Mu.

226
00:12:30,279 --> 00:12:31,039
Aren't you going to see me out?

227
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:34,279
Please.

228
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,440
Shaoze.

229
00:12:40,879 --> 00:12:42,440
How's it going between you and Jinxi?

230
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:44,039
As her eldest brother,

231
00:12:44,279 --> 00:12:46,320
I do hope to call you
my brother-in-law soon.

232
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,720
We have not seen each
other for so many years.

233
00:12:48,039 --> 00:12:49,200
We need to get to know each other more.

234
00:12:49,759 --> 00:12:52,600
After all, feelings
require mutual affection.

235
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:53,559
Right?

236
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:54,919
Jinchen.

237
00:13:02,519 --> 00:13:04,240
This is what happens
when you use Meiyan essence!

238
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,799
Everyone should see

239
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,000
how Meiyan International

240
00:13:07,399 --> 00:13:08,919
ruined my face with fake products!

241
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,159
You cannot even handle a woman?

242
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:11,600
What are you good for?

243
00:13:11,919 --> 00:13:12,799
The one causing trouble this time

244
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,039
is a beauty blogger

245
00:13:14,679 --> 00:13:15,679
with millions of followers.

246
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,960
She demands one million in compensation.

247
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:20,320
Otherwise, she'll make it public.

248
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:22,960
How dare she ask for such a huge sum?

249
00:13:25,559 --> 00:13:27,320
This is not the first time
we have encountered this.

250
00:13:27,919 --> 00:13:29,320
You know what to do.

251
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:30,600
But

252
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,200
she insists on meeting you.

253
00:13:32,399 --> 00:13:33,120
I don't think

254
00:13:33,679 --> 00:13:34,799
she will compromise easily.

255
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:36,919
Then give her the money.

256
00:13:37,519 --> 00:13:38,399
Our factory

257
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,720
is at a critical moment of expansion.

258
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,600
If anything goes wrong,

259
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:45,120
you will all suffer the consequences!

260
00:13:45,559 --> 00:13:46,039
Yes, sir.

261
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,720
I will ask her sign the agreement now.

262
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:57,820
(Relationship Chart)

263
00:13:57,820 --> 00:14:03,500
(Meiyan International; Raw Materials)

264
00:14:04,919 --> 00:14:06,440
Silence cost a million?

265
00:14:07,679 --> 00:14:09,039
It seems the raw materials
of Meiyan International

266
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:10,200
are suspicious.

267
00:14:13,039 --> 00:14:13,799
Next,

268
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,720
the real show is yet to come!

269
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:40,540
(Rehearsal in Progress)

270
00:14:40,540 --> 00:14:45,300
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

271
00:14:45,300 --> 00:14:50,140
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

272
00:14:50,140 --> 00:14:54,700
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

273
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:59,620
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

274
00:14:59,620 --> 00:15:03,420
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

275
00:15:03,420 --> 00:15:08,220
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

276
00:15:08,220 --> 00:15:11,060
♪Can't remember when
this flutter started♪

277
00:15:11,060 --> 00:15:13,740
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

278
00:15:14,100 --> 00:15:19,660
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

279
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:26,860
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

280
00:15:27,140 --> 00:15:31,820
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

281
00:15:31,980 --> 00:15:38,780
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

282
00:15:39,100 --> 00:15:45,900
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

283
00:15:46,100 --> 00:15:50,580
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

284
00:15:50,580 --> 00:15:53,940
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

285
00:15:53,940 --> 00:16:00,860
♪Right as I confess my love♪
